Maltese: Abel Hernández jindika għall-klub, U.S. Città di Palermo.
English: Abel Hernández plays for the club, U.S. Città di Palermo.

Maltese: William Anders kien membru tal-ekwipaġġ ta’ Apollo 8 (operat minn NASA) u bħala Kap tal-Uffiċċju tal-Astronaut fl-1976.
English: William Anders served as a crew member of Apollo 8 (operated by NASA) and as Chief of the Astronaut Office in 1976. His time in space is 8820.0 minutes. Frank Borman was also a crew member of Apollo 8.

Maltese: L-Esplussjoni tal-Bakon ġejja mill-Istati Uniti fejn Barack Obama huwa l-mexxej u l-Amerikan Ażjani jgħixu.
English: The Bacon Explosion comes from the United States where Barack Obama is the leader and Asian Americans live.

Maltese: Alexander Nouri huwa l-maniġer ta’ SV Werder Bremen II, l-ex-klub ta’ Aaron Hunt, li jindika għall-Vfl Wolfsburg.
English: Alexander Nouri is the manager for SV Werder Bremen II, the former club of Aaron Hunt, who plays for Vfl Wolfsburg. The league Vfl Wolfsburg play in is Bundesliga.

Maltese: Il-post tat-twelid ta’ Agustin Barboza huwa Asunción, il-Paraguay.
English: The birth place of Agustin Barboza is Asuncion, Paraguay.

Maltese: Il- perjodu orbitali għal 11264 Claudiomaccone huwa 1513. 722 jum.
English: The orbital period for 11264 Claudiomaccone is 1513.722 days.

Maltese: L-editur tal-AIP Advances huwa A.T. Charlie Johnson li jgħix fl-Istati Uniti u ħa għall-Università ta' Harvard.
English: The editor of AIP Advances is A.T. Charlie Johnson who lives in the U.S. and went to Harvard University.

Maltese: Is-sottopart tal-Amerika, NR-1, għandu veloċità massima ta’ 8.334 km/h u raġġ tal-bastiment ta’ 3.8 m.
English: The American submarine, NR-1, has a top speed of 8.334 km/h and a ship beam of 3.8 m.

Maltese: Alessandro Dal Canto huwa t-taħriġ tat-tim tal-futbol nazzjonali tal-Italja taħt is-17-il sena.
English: Alessandro Dal Canto is the coach of the Italy national under-17 football team.

Maltese: Abilene, it-Tessas jinsab fl-Istati Uniti, fejn l-Amerikan Ażjani huma grupp etniku.
English: Abilene, Texas is in the United States, where Asian Americans are an ethnic group.

Maltese: Il-munita ta’ Spanja hija l-Euro.
English: The currency of Spain is the Euro.

Maltese: Albert B. White, li twieled f’Cleveland, kien miżżewweġ ma’ Agnes Ward White u skema l-karriera tiegħu fl-4 ta’ Marzu 1905 u kien suċċessiv minn William M O Dawson.
English: Albert B. White, who was born in Cleveland, was married to Agnes Ward White and finished his career on March 4th 1905 and was succeeded by William M O Dawson.

Maltese: L-Università Cornell hija f’Ithaca, New York u hija affiljata mal-Assoċjazzjoni tal-Universitajiet Amerikani.
English: Cornell University is in Ithaca, New York and is affiliated with the Association of American Universities. Their nickname is Cornell Big Red and they publish the Administrative Science Quarterly.

Maltese: Aleksandra Kovac hija involuta b’mod mużiku ma’ Kristina Kovac u jindika mużika pop li l-fużjoni tagħha hija d-diska.
English: Aleksandra Kovac is musically involved with Kristina Kovac and plays pop music whose fusion is the disco.

Maltese: Ex-basketti tal-futbol tal-Italja taħt is-16-il sena, Alessio Romagnoli, jindika għall-klub A.C. Milan, li huwa ġestit minn Siniša Mihajlović u huwa fil-Liga Serie A.
English: Former Italian national under-16 football player, Alessio Romagnoli, plays for the club A.C. Milan, which is managed by Siniša Mihajlović and is in Serie A league.

Maltese: Il-post tal-Ajruport ta’ Aarhus huwa Tirstrup fir-reġjun ta’ Danimarka Ċentrali.
English: The location of Aarhus Airport is Tirstrup in the Central Denmark region.

Maltese: Il-Gvernatur tal-Karolina tat-Tramuntana Alfred Moore Scales huwa membru tal-Partit Demokratiku tal-Istati Uniti u kien segwit minn James Madison Leach.
English: Governor of North Carolina Alfred Moore Scales is a member of the U.S. Democratic Party and was succeeded by James Madison Leach.

Maltese: Il-klub ta’ Abel Hernandez huwa Penarol.
English: Abel Hernandez's club is Penarol.

Maltese: Il-popolazzjoni Ilocano u l-poplu Moro huma gruppi etniċi mill-Filippini, fejn l-Arabja hija waħda mill-lingwi mkellma u l-lottoj huwa ikla tradizzjonali.
English: The Ilocano people and the Moro people are ethnic groups from the Philippines, where Arabic is one of the languages spoken and batchoy is a traditional dish.
